 This code is a part of an admin panel for a FAQ (Frequently Asked Questions) system. It includes a top navigation bar that displays the current user's name, profile picture, and options to change password or log out. The navigation bar also has a language switcher dropdown menu that allows users to select their preferred language. Additionally, there is a session expiration counter that displays the remaining time until the user's session expires. Overall, this code provides a functional and user-friendly interface for managing FAQ content and user accounts.